  "html": "<section id=\"mme-scent-booster-lp\" style=\"margin:0; background:#EDEDED; color:#2b2b2b; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; line-height:1.6;\">\r\n\r\n    <div style=\"padding:40px 0; background:#ECDFC9;\" id=\"mme-sec-0\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #A1AB97; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(161,171,151,.15); overflow:hidden;\">\r\n          <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:22px; align-items:center; padding:35px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"flex:1 1 420px; min-width:280px;\">\r\n              <span style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:.78rem; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#A1AB97; background:#eaf5ef; padding:6px 12px; border-radius:999px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:15px;\">\r\n                Microplastic-Free Fragrance\r\n              </span>\r\n              <h1 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,3.8rem); line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 15px 0; color:#A1AB97; font-weight:400;\">\r\n                Scent Boosted. <br><span style=\"color:#BBC4B2;\">Planet Protected.</span>\r\n              </h1>\r\n              <p style=\"color:#5a6b63; font-size:1.15rem; margin-bottom:25px;\">\r\n                Infuse your laundry with a clean, <strong>mineral-based</strong> fragrance that lasts for weeks. Our microplastic-free beads dissolve completely, leaving only a fresh scent behind.\r\n              </p>\r\n              <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/laundry-scent-booster\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:18px 38px; border-radius:999px; background:#A1AB97; color:#fff; font-weight:800; text-decoration:none; box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(161,171,151,.3);\" data-gtm-cta=\"shopify\">\r\n                SHOP SCENT BOOSTERS\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n  \r\n            <div style=\"flex:1 1 420px; min-width:280px; position:relative;\">\r\n              <div style=\"border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #EDEDED;\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/IMG_0008_1_1728x.jpg?v=1768860714\" alt=\"MME Scent Booster\" style=\"width:100%; display:block;\">\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:15px; right:15px; width:120px; height:120px; border-radius:50%; border:5px solid #fff; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); overflow:hidden; background:#fff;\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/cdn/shop/files/4B5A5014_1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Scent Bead Detail\" style=\"width:100%; transform:scale(1.5);\">\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <div style=\"padding:60px 0; background:#fff; text-align:center;\" id=\"mme-sec-1\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; font-size:2.8rem; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:10px;\">Enduring Freshness</h2>\r\n        <p style=\"font-size:1.1rem; color:#5a6b63; margin-bottom:40px;\">Customizable intensity for every load.</p>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; gap:20px; margin:0 auto; max-width:600px;\">\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:4rem; font-weight:900; color:#A1AB97; line-height:1;\">250g</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:.9rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; font-weight:700;\">Weight</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div style=\"width:2px; height:80px; background:#BBC4B2;\"></div>\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:4rem; font-weight:900; color:#A1AB97; line-height:1;\">50</div>\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:.9rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; font-weight:700;\">Washes</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <p style=\"margin-top:35px; font-style:italic; color:#888;\">*Based on 5g (light scent) per standard load.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <div style=\"padding:60px 0; background:#EDEDED;\" id=\"mme-sec-2\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; text-align:center; font-size:2.5rem; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:40px;\">Simple Scent Enhancement</h2>\r\n        <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:30px;\">\r\n          <div style=\"text-align:center; padding:20px; background:#fff; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #A1AB97;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:900; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:10px;\">01. DOSE</div>\r\n            <p>Pour beads into the cap. Use 5g for light scent, 10g for medium, or 20g+ for maximum fragrance impact.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div style=\"text-align:center; padding:20px; background:#fff; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #A1AB97;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:900; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:10px;\">02. TOSS</div>\r\n            <p>Simply toss the beads directly into the empty drum of your machine before adding your laundry.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div style=\"text-align:center; padding:20px; background:#fff; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #A1AB97;\">\r\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:900; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:10px;\">03. ENJOY</div>\r\n            <p>Dual-fragrance technology releases scent bursts throughout the day as you move and fold your laundry.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <!-- CUSTOMER REVIEWS -->\r\n    <div style=\"padding:22px 0; background:#f3efe8;\" aria-label=\"Customer reviews\" id=\"mme-sec-3\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #d7c9b8; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(22,35,28,.10); padding:22px;\">\r\n          <p style=\"font-weight:800; color:#A1AB97; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; margin:0;\">What customers say</p>\r\n          <h2 style=\"margin:.2rem 0 0; font-size:1.5rem;\">Long-lasting freshness, no microplastics</h2>\r\n          <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"flex:1 1 300px; min-width:260px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #d7c9b8; border-radius:14px; padding:18px;\">\r\n              <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">Scent lasts for weeks</h3>\r\n              <div style=\"letter-spacing:2px; color:#f1b400; font-size:1.05rem;\">★★★★★</div>\r\n              <p style=\"color:#5a6b63; margin:8px 0;\">\"My laundry actually smells fresh for days after washing. The beads dissolve completely and there's no plastic—exactly what I was looking for.\"</p>\r\n              <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;\"><strong>— Claire Bennett</strong></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"flex:1 1 300px; min-width:260px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #d7c9b8; border-radius:14px; padding:18px;\">\r\n              <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">Easy to dose</h3>\r\n              <div style=\"letter-spacing:2px; color:#f1b400; font-size:1.05rem;\">★★★★★</div>\r\n              <p style=\"color:#5a6b63; margin:8px 0;\">\"I love that I can control how much scent I want per load. The mineral-based formula is gentle and the fragrance is clean, not overpowering.\"</p>\r\n              <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;\"><strong>— Miguel Santos</strong></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"flex:1 1 300px; min-width:260px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #d7c9b8; border-radius:14px; padding:18px;\">\r\n              <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">Planet-friendly choice</h3>\r\n              <div style=\"letter-spacing:2px; color:#f1b400; font-size:1.05rem;\">★★★★★</div>\r\n              <p style=\"color:#5a6b63; margin:8px 0;\">\"Finally a scent booster that doesn't use microplastics. Clothes smell amazing and I feel good about what goes down the drain. Will keep buying.\"</p>\r\n              <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;\"><strong>— Hannah Wright</strong></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"margin-top:16px; display:flex; justify-content:center;\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/laundry-scent-booster\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:14px 22px; border-radius:999px;\r\n                     background:linear-gradient(180deg,#A1AB97,#1e6e4b); color:#fff; font-weight:800; border:0;\r\n                     box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(22,35,28,.10); text-decoration:none; white-space:nowrap;\" data-gtm-cta=\"shopify\">\r\n              Shop Scent Boosters\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <div style=\"padding:60px 0; background:#fdfbf7;\" id=\"mme-sec-4\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:1140px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #A1AB97; border-radius:16px; padding:40px; border-left:10px solid #A1AB97;\">\r\n          <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; color:#A1AB97; margin-top:0;\">Technical Ingredient Transparency</h2>\r\n          <p style=\"margin-bottom:25px; color:#5a6b63;\">We prioritize <strong>mineral-based</strong> carriers and biodegradable fragrance technology.</p>\r\n          \r\n          <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap:20px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEDED; padding-bottom:10px;\">\r\n              <strong style=\"color:#A1AB97; display:block;\">Corn Extracts</strong>\r\n              Mineral-based carrier used to hold and release fragrance safely.\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEDED; padding-bottom:10px;\">\r\n              <strong style=\"color:#A1AB97; display:block;\">Bentonite</strong>\r\n              A mineral used to provide structure and support even distribution.\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEDED; padding-bottom:10px;\">\r\n              <strong style=\"color:#A1AB97; display:block;\">Encapsulated Scent</strong>\r\n              Friction-activated technology that releases scent throughout the day.\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #EDEDED; padding-bottom:10px;\">\r\n              <strong style=\"color:#A1AB97; display:block;\">Plastic-Free</strong>\r\n              Zero microplastics or synthetic dyes that linger in our waterways.\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <div style=\"padding:60px 0; background:#fff;\" id=\"mme-sec-5\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <div style=\"max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px;\">\r\n        <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; text-align:center; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:30px;\">Common Questions</h2>\r\n        \r\n        <details style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #EDEDED; padding:15px 0; cursor:pointer;\">\r\n          <summary style=\"font-weight:700; color:#2b2b2b;\">What are scent booster beads?</summary>\r\n          <p style=\"padding-top:10px; color:#5a6b63;\">Scent beads are small, mineral-based pearls designed to dissolve in the wash and infuse fabrics with long-lasting fragrance.</p>\r\n        </details>\r\n        \r\n        <details style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #EDEDED; padding:15px 0; cursor:pointer;\">\r\n          <summary style=\"font-weight:700; color:#2b2b2b;\">Are these safe for sensitive skin?</summary>\r\n          <p style=\"padding-top:10px; color:#5a6b63;\">Our formula is <strong>plant-derived</strong> and free from harsh dyes or phosphonates, making it gentler than traditional laundry fragrances.</p>\r\n        </details>\r\n        \r\n        <details style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #EDEDED; padding:15px 0; cursor:pointer;\">\r\n          <summary style=\"font-weight:700; color:#2b2b2b;\">How long does the scent last?</summary>\r\n          <p style=\"padding-top:10px; color:#5a6b63;\">Under proper storage, the friction-activated scent particles can keep laundry smelling fresh for up to 12 weeks.</p>\r\n        </details>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n    <div style=\"padding:80px 0; text-align:center; background:#ECDFC9;\" id=\"mme-sec-6\" class=\"mme-scroll-target\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif; font-size:2.5rem; color:#A1AB97; margin-bottom:20px;\">Ready for long-lasting freshness?</h2>\r\n      <a href=\"https://memotherearthbrand.com/products/laundry-scent-booster\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:20px 50px; border-radius:999px; background:#A1AB97; color:#fff; font-weight:800; text-decoration:none; font-size:1.2rem; box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(161,171,151,.4);\" data-gtm-cta=\"shopify\">\r\n        ADD TO CART\r\n      </a>\r\n      <p style=\"margin-top:20px; font-size:0.85rem; color:#5a6b63;\">Microplastic-free. Vegan. Earth-friendly.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  \r\n  </section>",
